<LegalPage eyebrow="Help" heading="Shipping & Returns" lede="We want you to love what you ordered. If something isn&rsquo;t right, we&rsquo;ll make it easy to sort out.">
  <h2>Shipping</h2>
  <p>We ship worldwide. Shipping is free across Hong Kong and India. For all other destinations, shipping costs are calculated at checkout based on your location.</p>
  <p>Most orders arrive within 2 weeks. During busy periods, allow a little extra time. If your order is time-sensitive, write to us at <a href="mailto:order@mirkash.com">order@mirkash.com</a> before placing it and we&rsquo;ll do our best to prioritise it.</p>
  <p>Once your order is dispatched, you&rsquo;ll receive a tracking link by email.</p>
  <p>Please note that international orders may be subject to customs duties on arrival. These are determined by your local customs authority and are the responsibility of the customer.</p>

  <h2>Returns</h2>
  <p>You have 14 days from delivery to return your bag for a full refund. No long explanations needed &mdash; just let us know.</p>
  <p>To be eligible, the bag must be unused and returned in its original packaging, with the box, dust bag, and all inserts included. Items that show signs of use cannot be accepted.</p>
  <p>Return shipping costs are borne by the customer. We recommend a tracked and insured service &mdash; we can&rsquo;t take responsibility for items lost on their way back to us.</p>
  <p>To start a return, visit our <a href="/pages/returns-portal">returns portal</a> or write to <a href="mailto:order@mirkash.com">order@mirkash.com</a> with your order number. Once we receive and inspect the bag, your refund will be processed within 14 working days to your original payment method.</p>
  <p>We don&rsquo;t offer direct exchanges. Return your original order and place a new one at your convenience.</p>
  <p><a href="/pages/returns-portal">Start a return &rarr;</a></p>

  <h2>Warranty</h2>
  <p>Every Mir Kash bag is backed by a 1-year warranty against manufacturing defects &mdash; stitching, hardware, structural issues. If something isn&rsquo;t right, write to us at <a href="mailto:order@mirkash.com">order@mirkash.com</a>. We&rsquo;ll assess it and either repair or replace it.</p>
  <p>The warranty does not cover wear from regular use, accidental damage, or misuse.</p>

  <p><strong>Questions?</strong> <a href="mailto:order@mirkash.com">order@mirkash.com</a></p>
</LegalPage>
